Use 'sdg-docs' to browse documentation from all installed modules
Use 'sdg-docs --from SDG-DOC-DEVS' to browse only developer docs
Use 'sdg-docs sources' to list all documentation modules
Use 'sdg-docs links' to open external reference documentation
Documentation modules are identified by their SDG-DOC- prefix
Each module ships its own docs to ~/.local/docs/ automatically
